 and\nat least $1.3\\times$ reduction of both the computation and communication\noverheads in the implementation of non-linear layers under different data\ndimensions. Meanwhile, SIMC 2.0 demonstrates an encouraging runtime boost by\n$2.3\\sim 4.3\\times$ over SIMC on different state-of-the-art ML models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 Jul 2022 05:33:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 27 Oct 2022 13:19:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-28"}
