o spectroscopically probe the nature of the earliest\ngalaxies, both the short timescales associated with pristine systems and\nambiguities in interpreting key diagnostic emission lines may hinder progress.\nSpecial care will be needed before claiming the discovery of systems with pure\nPop. III stars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 Jul 2022 10:28:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-12"}
